    .docs-content
      h1 Badge Component
      p Badge component represents badge element that can be used in lists, links, navigation bars, etc.
      h2 Usage example
      pre
        code
          | &lt;f7-badge&gt;5&lt;/f7-badge&gt;
          | &lt;!--
          | Renders to:
          | &lt;span class="badge"&gt;5&lt;/f7-badge&gt;
          | --&gt;
          | 
          | &lt;f7-badge color="red"&gt;5&lt;/f7-badge&gt;
          | &lt;!--
          | Renders to:
          | &lt;span class="badge color-red"&gt;5&lt;/f7-badge&gt;
          | --&gt;
